verbiste.el is a package allowing to use the [http://perso.b2b2c.ca/~sarrazip/dev/verbiste.html verbiste] program to conjugate/deconjugate French verbs.

It is available in:

* Git: https://salsa.debian.org/debian/verbiste/-/blob/master/debian/verbiste.el
* Debian: https://tracker.debian.org/pkg/elpa-verbiste

I have made a different version which has (I think) a nicer display:

http://kanis.fr/hg/lisp/ivan/verbiste.el

http://kanis.fr/verbiste.jpg

